  "title": "WAREHOUSE ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<p>POSSESS FORKLIFT LICENSE PREFERENCE.</p><p>• ABLE TO PERFORM PHYSICAL, HANDS-ON WAREHOUSE HAND TASKS AS ASSIGNED.</p><p>• BILINGUAL SPEAKING (FOR  COMMUNICATION WITH COLLEAGUES)</p><p>•ASSIST IN HANDLING INDOOR PACKING ACTIVITIES.</p><p>• PICK UP GOODS & PLACE THEM IN DESIGNATED LOCATIONS TO BE READY FOR COLLECTION OR DAILY DELIVERIES.</p><p>• ENSURE PACKING LISTS (OR PICK LISTS) ARE PROCESSED 100% ACCURATELY AND ON TIME FOR COLLECTION OR DELIVERY.</p><p>• ASSIST DELIVERY DRIVER TO CHECK & LOAD GOODS UNTO VAN OR TRUCK.</p><p>• STACKING INCOMING GOODS ONTO PALLETS AND TRANSPORTING THEM TO THE DESIGNATED SHELF LOCATION.</p><p>• REPACKING OF BLISTER PACKS, BUNDLE ND ETC.</p><p>• OTHER DUTIES THAT MAY BE ASSIGNED FROM TIME TO TIME BY THE SUPERIOR.</p><p>• Able to work independently</p>",
